name: XOXO U
description:
How many of us feel anxious of being us?. Somehow it's hurt to know the fact that society rolling in the way they want. All girls should have this all girls should have that. We can't just becoming what we want. Too many rules to obey, I choose freedom. I choose to love myself, follow me?.

This special drop was drop in to celebrate valentines day as a freedom person, as a person who belong to the inner selves. To understand ourselves more and to be aware about what we want rather than just pleasing others. 

For those who just purchase this artwork feel free to adapt it and print it to stickers, greeting card, or part of an art collage works. spread the love, spread the freedom. 

XOXO_Desh
